OL,3,CMen's first team lead tributes to 15-
OL,4,Cyear-old Academy player after tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FOxford United's men's first team have
OL,8,Fheld a minute's silence in memory of
OL,9,F15-year-old Academy player Amelia
OL,10,FAplin, as tributes pour in from across
OL,11,Fthe sporting community following her
OL,12,Fsudden death.
OL,14,FThe tribute took place at the club's
OL,15,Ftraining ground on Monday morning,
OL,16,Fwhere players and coaching staff stood
OL,17,Fin a silent circle to honour the
OL,18,Fteenager.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
