OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773144738
OL,3,CMen's first team lead tributes to 15-
OL,4,Cyear-old Academy player after tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAmelia, a talented goalkeeper, was
OL,8,Fplaying for the Girls' Academy against
OL,9,FFulham at the Horspath training centre
OL,10,Fon Saturday, March 7, when she
OL,11,Fsuffered a "serious medical incident."
OL,13,FDespite the immediate efforts of
OL,14,Fmedical staff from both clubs and the
OL,15,Femergency services, the club confirmed
OL,16,Fon Sunday that Amelia had passed away.
OL,18,FBeyond her role at Oxford United,
OL,19,FAmelia was part of the Junior Premier
OL,20,FLeague All Stars program.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773144738
OL,3,CMen's first team lead tributes to 15-
OL,4,Cyear-old Academy player after tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMartin Brock, chief executive of the
OL,8,FJPL, described her as a "leader and a
OL,9,Fbright light," adding that her loss
OL,10,Fleaves a "void that words cannot
OL,11,Fadequately fill."
OL,13,F"Amelia represented everything we hope
OL,14,Fto see in a young footballer:
OL,15,Fresilience, passion, and a strong team
OL,16,Fspirit," a JPL statement read. "As a
OL,17,Fgoalkeeper, she played with courage
OL,18,Fand determination and was a constant
OL,19,Fsource of encouragement to her
OL,20,Fteammates."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
