PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773144738
OL,3,CMen's first team lead tributes to 15-
OL,4,Cyear-old Academy player after tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FShe had represented the club at County
OL,8,Fand Regional championships, as well as
OL,9,Fthe National Cup Final in the Arena
OL,10,FLeague. "This is an unimaginable loss
OL,11,Fand Amelia will be truly missed," the
OL,12,Fclub said in a statement. "Our deepest
OL,13,Fcondolences and thoughts go out to her
OL,14,Ffamily and friends."
OL,16,FGrassroots clubs across the region
OL,17,Fhave also joined the mourning.
OL,18,FSummertown Stars Football Club noted
OL,19,Fthat moments like this serve as a
OL,20,Freminder that the game is about
OL,21,F"community" above all else.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
